# merge branches
1. fast forward merge
git merge --ff-only <branch>
$ git merge <branch>

2. merging changes in different files
create a new merge commit
$ git merge <branch>

3. merging changes in different lines
$ git merge <branch>

4. merging conflicting changes
$ git merge <branch>
$ git mergetool   --> diff-gui
$ git commit

